### Variables
@host = http://localhost:9082

### Get Hello Message
GET {{host}}/hello
Accept: application/json

### Echo Message (Empty body)
POST {{host}}/echo
Content-Type: application/json

### Echo Message with Text
POST {{host}}/echo
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello, this is a test message!

### Echo Message with JSON
POST {{host}}/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Hello from JSON",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-23T19:26:16+05:30"
}

### Get SNMP System Info (Default parameters)
GET {{host}}/snmp/info

### Get SNMP System Info (Custom parameters)
GET {{host}}/snmp/info?host=localhost&community=public&oid=1.3.6.1.2.1.1.1.0
